Microservices:

Rather than giving into single product to customer you are going to divide that product into smaller components
spilliting into different components based on functionality 

lifecycle automation(ci/cd)
scalbilit(if we want to spin up_
developer independence(if devloper want to devlop new instance)

microservice solution using docker

1)compose the application using docker
2)break the application componenets into individual containers
3)store the changeable data as volumes in external volumes







